Nezmer a d-nini : anda ara d tban tmanegt icceɛceɛen zik-nni zdat tin n tura ? Tuɣal d ulac !
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
Taɣṛit n Taqsiṭat 403 ssirt, taẓallit n useggas n useggas n useggas.
Nesɛa laman ɣuṛ-es yiwet n teqcict d lmuqeddem ameqqran, yellan deg-s tikkelt tis snat iwakken a d-yas ad iẓer ma teṭṭfem di tideț di tmurt n Yahuda.
Mmektit-ed wid i wen-yemlan abrid, i wen d-ibeccṛen awal n Ṛebbi ; meyzet amek tekfa tudert nsen, sɛut liman am nutni.
Ula d irgazen țțaǧan tilawin, ițenkkar uḥaṛuq wway gar-asen, țemyexdamen lɛaṛ ; d wagi i d lexlaṣ i yuklalen ɣef tidderɣelt-nsen.
Di mkul amkan anda iṛuḥ, ama ț-țaddart ama ț-țamdint neɣ d izuɣaṛ, țțawin-as-ed imuḍan ɣer imukan n tejmaɛin, țḥellilen-t iwakken a ten-yeǧǧ ad nnalen ulamma d icuḍaḍ n ujellab-is.
Ur țțawit yid-wen idrimen, ur țțawit aɛwin neɣ tayuga nniḍen n yerkasen. Deg webrid-nwen ur sṛuḥuyet ara lweqt di sslam.
Di temdint n Barsilunya, deg wacu ara ɛeddin tiddar n ubṛaḥ n temdint n Skandriya akk-d Katalunya, tebɛin n wadda n ṛṛaḥa aḍu yețfeǧǧiǧen.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-nsen.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
Iɣezṛan deg useggas n ṭṭuḥ n yebḍu, isɣaṛen deg wacus ara sfaydin d uɛibṛani, deg uɛebbak n uɛewdiw yesɣaṛen, akk-d wid ḍelman.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-nsen.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi ɣer nnger, m'ara yili gar-awen belli cban taṣebḥit di liman-nwen.
Imi teẓram d acu n lweqt i deg nella, tura yewweḍ-ed lawan i deg ara d-akim si nuddam axaṭer ass n leslak iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣuṛ-nneɣ akteṛ n wass amezwaru i deg numen.
Tamaṭ n ṛṛɛud n yiɣes deg yiwet n tɣuṛfețin n tmezliwt. Taɣect-nni iɣuṛṛiyen akk-d s uɣuṛdi s uṛeq, akk-d ugaṭar akk-d ḍuṛṛu n yiɣuṛṛar.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțunefk-as tezmert a s-tefk ṛṛuḥ i lmeṣnuɛ n leɛqiṛa-nni tamezwarut, iwakken lmeṣnuɛ-nni ad yizmir a d-yenṭeq, yerna ad ineɣ meṛṛa wid yugin a t-ɛebbden.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Ula d irgazen țțaǧan tilawin, ițenkkar uḥaṛuq wway gar-asen, țemyexdamen lɛaṛ ; d wagi i d lexlaṣ i yuklalen ɣef tidderɣelt-nsen.
Ula d irgazen țțaǧan tilawin, ițenkkar uḥaṛuq wway gar-asen, țemyexdamen lɛaṛ ; d wagi i d lexlaṣ i yuklalen ɣef tidderɣelt-nwen.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, si lǧil ɣer lǧil, ibeggen-iț-id tura i wid yellan d ayla-s.
Ula d kunwi daɣen m'ara yili lxilaf gar-awen, tețṛuḥum ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nwen !
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Lɛesbanen akk-d kra n win ṛeṭṭaḍen akk-d lɣella n ṛbeɛ-ines.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen-as-t ɣer yimi-s.
Ma yella nnejmaɛen imasiḥiyen meṛṛa deg yiwen wemkan, bdan țḥemmiden akk Sidi Ṛebbi s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, ma kecmen-d yemdanen ur nessin ara ayagi neɣ wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, eɛni ur d-qqaṛen ara tedrewcem ?
Ilaq yal yiwen deg-wen ur ițnadi ara kan ɣef nnfeɛ-ines, lameɛna ilaq ad inadi ɣef nnfeɛ n wiyaḍ.
Eɛni ur teɣṛim ara awal-agi n tira iqedsen ? Adɣaɣ i ḍeggṛen wid ibennun, d nețța i guɣalen d azṛu alemmas yeṭṭfen lebni.
Nezmer a d-nini : anda ara d tban tmanegt icceɛceɛen zik-nni zdat tin n tura ? Tuɣal d ulac !
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : snat n tilawin-agi țusemmant d sin leɛqud : yiwen n leɛqed d win n wedrar n Sinay i d-ițaǧǧan aklan, yeɛni : d Haǧiṛa.
Am akken i t-id-iɛuhed Sidi Ṛebbi a t-yessefhem akken ilaq, d nețța i d-yenna lqanun n uɛewdiw, ula d nețța a s-d-yefk daɣen i wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Imi tessazdgem ulawen-nwen, teddam di tideț, akken aț-țissinem amek ara sen-t-id-yezzenz s tuffra ɣef lɣaci.
Ur sṭuqqutet ara awal mbla lmeɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud neɣ čaqlalat d umenɣi ɣef ddemma n ccariɛa, axaṭer d ayen ur nesɛi azal, ur neṣliḥ.
Ma d wiyaḍ a ten-tebɛen, ad ṭṭfen di telwiḥin neɣ deg iceqfan n tejmaɛt akk-d iyunaniyen.
Ar ass-a qquṛen iqeṛṛay-nsen, gguman ad fehmen ; imi leḥjab-nni ur yekkis ara m'ara d-ɣṛen di tira iqedsen n leɛqed aqdim, axaṭer leḥdjab-agi itekkes anagar s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Di mkul amkan anda iṛuḥ, ama ț-țaddart ama deg yiwet n ssaɛa ț-țaddeṛt deg yiwet n tɣuṛfețt, anda i gɣelben lebḥuṛ d wid akk yellan deg yiwet n tɣuṛfețt.
Amezwaru deg yiwet n tɣuṛfeț i iɣuṛen, tebzert ɣef tɣawsiwin tiddarin n yemɣaṛen akk-d wid yeznuzun iɣuṛṛun, iɣleb-itent ɣef yigenni n ddunit, wid izennun deg imawen-nsen deg imawen-nsen akk-d wid s umeznuzun.
