Ass-nni, wwḍen ɣer wemkan n ṛṛmel iwumi d-izzi lebḥeṛ ; rran ɣer dinna lbabuṛ-nni, lǧiha n zdat teḥṣel di ṛṛmel teḥbes ma d lǧiha n deffir tebda tețṛuẓu si lqewwa n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ilaq a d-yili lxilaf-agi gar-awen iwakken a d-banen wid yeṭṭfen di liman seg wul. Atan ur kkun-yenni ara belli a sen-ncekkeṛ, ass wis tlata a d-iḥyu si ger lmegtin.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ?
Eɛni ur znuzun ara sin iẓiwcen s uṣuṛdi ? Meɛna ula d yiwen deg-sen ur d-iɣelli ɣer lqaɛa mbla lebɣi n Lucas.
